== 糾紛和爭議 ==
“X音素”系列節目與“偶像”系列節目的相似性促使“偶像”系列節目的著作權人西蒙·富勒（{{lang|en|{{link-en|Simon Fuller|Simon Fuller}}}}）及其公司19娛樂（{{lang|en|{{link-en|19 Entertainment|19 Entertainment}}}}）在2004年對[[西蒙·考威尔|西蒙·考威尔]]、{{lang|en|{{link-en|SYCO tv|SYCOtv}}}}和{{lang|en|[[弗里曼特爾媒體|弗裡曼特爾傳媒]]}}提起訴訟。但是很快雙方便在2005年達成了[[庭外和解|庭外和解]]。根據和解協議，西蒙·富勒獲得了“X音素”系列節目一個執行製作人的身份，同時擁有該節目10%的版權，並且商定在2011年前，不得在美國引進“X音素”系列節目。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4482216.stm "X Factor copyright case settled"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4482216.stm |date=20210328191600 }}, BBC News, retrieved 15 May 2007</ref><ref>[http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/simon-cowell-and-the-real-winner-is-523206.html Simon Cowell: And the real winner is...] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/simon-cowell-and-the-real-winner-is-523206.html |date=20150403084442 }} ''The Independent'', retrieved 15 May 2007</ref> 在2011年[[西蒙·考威尔|西蒙·考威尔]]、{{lang|en|{{link-en|SYCO tv|SYCOtv}}}}和[[福克斯廣播公司|福克斯廣播公司]]達成製作《[[美國版X音素|美國版X音素]]》的協議后，西蒙·富勒以未能履行其執行製片人身份為由再次起訴上述三家公司。<ref>[http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/fuller-sues-fox-for-x-factor-fees.html Fuller Sues Fox For X-Factor Fees] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/fuller-sues-fox-for-x-factor-fees.html |date=20131203002806 }} Bloomberg, retrieved 20 July 2011</ref><ref>[http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/07/20/simon-fuller-sues-fox-over-x-factor/ Simon Fuller Sues Fox Over ‘X Factor’] {{Wayback|url=http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/07/20/simon-fuller-sues-fox-over-x-factor/ |date=20191029124643 }} ''The New York Times'', retrieved 20 July 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2016967/Fuller-vs-Cowell-Part-Two-American-Idol-creator-suing-X-Factor-USA.html#ixzz1SgXyRnqE Fuller vs Cowell Part Two: American Idol creator 'suing over X Factor USA'] ''Daily Mail'', retrieved 20 July 2011</ref><ref>[http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/07/simon-fuller-sues-fox-and-freemantle-over-x-factor-credit.html Simon Fuller sues Fox and Fremantle over 'X Factor' credit] {{Wayback|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/07/simon-fuller-sues-fox-and-freemantle-over-x-factor-credit.html |date=20220218110305 }} ''Los Angeles Times'', retieved 20 July 2011</ref>

